data.description:
Prepare to be Moved! Welcome to 9516 Snow Rd. Parma, Ohio, a charming colonial-style home with plenty of character and modern amenities! Located in close proximity to Cleveland Metroparks, restaurants, shopping, hospitals, and I-480, this house has everything a modern family needs. Step into the main floor and be awed by the hardwood floors and ornamental moldings throughout. The updated kitchen offers 14-inch tile flooring, granite countertops, a tasteful tile backsplash, beautiful cabinetry with a built-in wine rack, and stainless-steel appliances including a touchless kitchen faucet. The living room flows seamlessly into the dining room, where you can access the backyard. Enjoy the finished basement with a full bath. On the second floor, there are three spacious bedrooms and a second updated bath with a waterfall shower and gorgeous tilework. The stone accents on the
front of the house add character to an already charming home. Out back, you will find a fully fenced yard with an above-ground pool with a wrap-around deck, a shed for extra storage, and an additional deck with a pergola. Picture yourself soaking in the sun while cooling off in your private pool on a hot summer day! You are sure to enjoy your downtime with this move-in-ready home. Don't miss this opportunity to own an amazing property!
